168
00:10:43,351 --> 00:10:44,393
[Haesang grunts]

169
00:10:45,728 --> 00:10:47,229
-[Hyunwoo's father] Damn it!
-[crying]

170
00:10:47,313 --> 00:10:48,606
[Hyunwoo's father] Don't do it!

171
00:10:48,689 --> 00:10:50,316
Let me help you.

172
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:51,734
