01:03:27,345 --> 01:03:30,515
YEAR 1958, JANGJIN-RI

1008
01:03:37,772 --> 01:03:38,981
[owl hoots]

1009
01:03:45,571 --> 01:03:47,573
[♪ suspenseful music]

